quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  50,16,"Dájúdájú A ṣẹ̀dá ènìyàn. A sì mọ ohun tí ẹ̀mí rẹ̀ ń sọ fún un ní ròyíròyí. Àwa sì súnmọ́ ọn ju isan ọrùn rẹ̀.{1}.",footnotes:1:Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Mujādilah;58:7.
  50,17,"(Rántí) nígbà tí (mọlāika) àwọn olùgbọ̀rọ̀-sílẹ̀ méjì bá bẹ̀rẹ̀sí gba ọ̀rọ̀ (sílẹ̀), tí ọ̀kan jókòó sí ọ̀tún, tí ọ̀kan jókòó sí òsì."
  50,18,"(Ẹnì kan) kò sì níí sọ ọ̀rọ̀ kan àyàfi kí ẹ̀ṣọ́ kan ti wà níkàlẹ̀ pẹ̀lú rẹ̀ (fún àkọsílẹ̀ rẹ̀)."
  51,10,"Ègbé ni fún àwọn òpùrọ́;"
  51,11,"àwọn tí wọ́n wà nínú àìmọ̀kan tó gbópọn tí wọ́n ti gbàgbéra."
  51,12,"tí wọ́n ń bèèrè ìgbà tí Ọjọ́ Ẹ̀san máa ṣẹlẹ̀."
  52,1,"Allāhu fi àpáta Tūr búra."
  52,2,"Ó tún fi Tírà tí wọ́n kọ n̄ǹkan sínú rẹ̀ búra ."
  52,3,"(Wọ́n kọ̀ ọ́) sínú n̄ǹkan ìkọ̀wé tí wọ́n tẹ́ ojú rẹ̀ sílẹ̀."